/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6835af7cd037bf92d230463468db40677e50d048","tid":216244,"uid":29947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T04:52:29.000Z","msg":"我初初都唔信 之後俾我發現真係呃我好多嘢 <br />\n過來人勸你真係要相信女人直覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一定做左d嘢令你懷疑既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依d男人 玩下好了 唔好咁上心 唔好過人世"},{"pid":"0f85814842487ff9c7b926b6d804cb455ed20ca7","tid":216244,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T04:58:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你地幾歲？</blockquote><br />\n廿幾</blockquote><br />\n情侶越細個分手機會越高<br />\n畀人屌下就算啦<br />\n將來？不了</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁唔通三十歲個d先係認真咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你認真都冇用，到最後九成都係分手，叫你唔好諗將來啫</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  係因為太細？ <br />\n我對佢好認真想有將來架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲要問點解 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 會唔會太蠢"},{"pid":"cbeb4c7c54c3f0394548f25b1c0b4b0260f8459b","tid":216244,"uid":110135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T05:00:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我初初都唔信 之後俾我發現真係呃我好多嘢 <br />\n過來人勸你真係要相信女人直覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一定做左d嘢令你懷疑既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依d男人 玩下好了 唔好咁上心 唔好過人世</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點樣發現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實佢係凌晨返工既<br />\n佢平時放假會同我講 但係有一日無 最尾我係見到佢手機同人請假先知佢放左假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後我問佢 佢有少少燥底咁屌左我兩個 話唔係下下都可以全部野交代哂<br />\n<br />\n仲有就係佢試過幾次電話無開 完全搵佢唔到 <br />\n當時我有上佢屋企搵佢 因為佢要返工 好彩佢係屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但會諗有無收埋其他女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺得自己好有問題 我坦白同佢講過我有咁諗 佢話佢唔會咁做 如果有第二個一定係分左手先會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a7662c31ab478dcd50d58f605f2a4c5375f916d","tid":216244,"uid":14440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T05:50:03.000Z","msg":"信任係建立出黎 無可能空手套白狼"},{"pid":"c5a52ac5391519eece8b9c9593a13b0baf6500bb","tid":216244,"uid":91968,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T06:58:35.000Z","msg":"我都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然佢成日安撫我 <br />\n但係唔知點解內心依然都係好驚好不安<br />\n男朋友拍拖2個月就話想同我結婚<br />\n聽完係好開心 不過又會開始擔心佢係咪純粹講下<br />\n我越愛佢就越擔驚受怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84d54e036c1ff6bf9aba75ab51a28f3747adac4c","tid":216244,"uid":60611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T08:20:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我同男朋友啱啱開始無幾耐<br />\n唔知點解成日都唔信佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日會驚佢唔知去左邊<br />\n佢會同朋友返大陸揼骨<br />\n我覺得自己好多疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日驚佢會去叫雞同有其他女<br />\n可以點？<br />\n男人係咪好憎女人咁多疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n錯左一次 個信任真係會好難建立番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"401324dc3c8369805e4fdf09419b5ddf59d43c92","tid":216244,"uid":110135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T10:16:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.